snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard: Australian biosecurity
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard: Australian biosecurity is a triumph of minimalist cinema that has forced its way into the pantheon of movie history in a matter of minutes.The 42-second magnum opus proves Johnny Depp, husband to Australia's most famous immigration card falsifier Amber Heard, is back at the top of his game
